# Architecture

Three VirtualBox VMs:

- Kali Linux (attacker)
- Windows 11 (victim)
- Ubuntu Server 26.04 (Wazuh SIEM)

## Network

Two adapters per VM:

- Adapter 1: Bridged (internet + access from my host)
- Adapter 2: Internal Network "SOC-LAB" (isolated VM communication)

## IPs on the internal network (SOC-LAB)

- Kali: 192.168.100.10
- Ubuntu Wazuh: 192.168.100.20
- Windows: 192.168.100.30

